description:
Parkour?! Donkour?!! Today we focus on getting our important key farms going for the season by building a Wither Skeleton farm and Gold farm. We make a deal with Impulse to get Shulker Shells. This pushes us to build our main storage room so we can start mass collecting things and get organized.
